OL,5,G2100 999: Critical Condition
OL,6,     FOn the front line at Birmingham's
OL,7,     FQueen Elizabeth Hospital. A man
OL,8,     Ffalls from scaffold, impaling
OL,9,     Fhimself on a flagpole, and a
OL,10,     F73-year-old faces life-changing
OL,11,     Finjuries.
OL,12,G2200 A&E After Dark
OL,13,     FSecurity are called when a patient
OL,14,     Fis abusive to the nurses and
OL,15,     Fdoctors and Emma arrives by air
OL,16,     Fambulance after falling 30 feet
OL,17,     Foff a castle wall.
