OL,5,G2300 Trauma Room One
OL,6,     FSeries that takes us deep inside
OL,7,     Fthe gripping high-stakes world of
OL,8,     Fbrain and spinal surgery at The
OL,9,     FWalton Centre in Liverpool.
OL,10,     FChristine has broken her neck - a
OL,11,     Flife-threatening injury. (Ep1)
OL,12,G0000 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FDr Toby Nelson checks a patient's
OL,14,     Fback and finds a pre-cancerous
OL,15,     Fmole, Dr Emma McMullen inspects a
OL,16,     Flipoma on a patient's buttock, and
OL,17,     FDr Dev Shah treats a collection of
OL,18,     Fskin tags.
