OL,5,G0100 Dirty Home Rescue
OL,6,     FThe team help out a woman whose
OL,7,     Ftwo-bedroom flat is overflowing
OL,8,     Fwith stuff she doesn't have time
OL,9,     Fto clean between her two jobs and
OL,10,     Fstudying for a degree.
OL,11,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,12,     FAs a heatwave hits Yorkshire, the
OL,13,     Fpatient numbers rise with the
OL,14,     Ftemperature. Documentary series
OL,15,     Ffilmed inside Barnsley casualty
OL,16,     Fdepartment.
OL,17,G0245 Scam City: Don't Get Caught Out!
OL,18,     FIn Istanbul, a friendly
OL,19,     Fconversation at night may lead to
OL,20,     Fa bar bill of hundreds or even
OL,21,     Fthousands. If you can't pay,
OL,22,     Fyou're threatened with violence.
